TestPerActionErrorScope
/ Verifies error modifier applies only to its action, not subsequent actions.
/ Step 1's handler (MarkHandled) fires because MayFail throws.
/ Step 2's handler (ignore) is independent — doesn't use step 1's handler.
- set %handled% = false
- call MayFail
    on error call MarkHandled
- call AlwaysFails
    on error ignore
- assert %handled% equals true

MayFail
/ This goal fails — error modifier on step 1 should catch it
- throw error 'first action error'

MarkHandled
- set %handled% = true

AlwaysFails
- throw error 'second action error'
